Comment: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:10.19,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\3c&HCEBDEF&}1  已被拆穿的伪笑
Comment: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.98,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\3c&H847EE8&}2  针对于你的怄气
Comment: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:18.15,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\3c&H8F83CE&}3  快点察觉 这份不加掩饰的爱恋
Comment: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.95,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\3c&H7796EA&}4  向着过去蓦然回首
Comment: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:24.54,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\3c&H9A79E1&}5  这份心意早已传达
Comment: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:30.83,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,博览群书却也无法理解的恋慕
Comment: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.34,op-cn - 1,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an1}{\3c&HB79B6C&}最初的厌恶
Comment: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.55,op-cn - 2,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an3}{\3c&HB79B6C&}最初的厌恶
Comment: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.26,op-cn - 1,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an1}{\3c&HB79B6C&}如今的思慕
Comment: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.47,op-cn - 2,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an3}{\3c&HB79B6C&}如今的思慕
Comment: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:42.76,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,请不要打破这般天作之合
Comment: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.31,op-cn - 1,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an1}{\3c&HB79B6C&}无论发生何事
Comment: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.56,op-cn - 2,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an3}{\3c&HB79B6C&}无论发生何事
Comment: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.31,op-cn - 1,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an1}{\3c&HB79B6C&}只要能够
Comment: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.44,op-cn - 2,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an3}{\3c&HB79B6C&}只要能够
Comment: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:51.15,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,传达至你的耳边
Comment: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:51.77,op-cn - 1,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an8}{\3c&HCEBDEF&}我
Comment: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.27,op-cn - 2,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an8}{\3c&H847EE8&}我
Comment: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:52.77,op-cn - 3,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an8}{\3c&H8F83CE&}我
Comment: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.31,op-cn - 4,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an8}{\3c&H7796EA&}我
Comment: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\3c&H9A79E1&}我一直思念着你
